  "response": "Yes, boys can certainly experience being \"friendzoned.\" The term refers to a situation where one person expresses romantic interest in another, but the other person only wants to maintain a platonic friendship. This phenomenon can happen to anyone, regardless of gender. It's important to remember that feelings and relationships can be complex, and not everyone's romantic feelings align. Open communication about intentions and feelings can help clarify relationships and avoid potential misunderstandings.",
